OL,7,FThe family of a hospital manager who
OL,8,Fcollapsed and later died while on a
OL,9,Fcall to NHS staff say he has been "let
OL,10,Fdown" by the organisation he worked
OL,11,Ffor.
OL,13,FThe coroner's court in Winchester
OL,14,Fheard Nicholas Ginger from Shirley,
OL,15,FSouthampton, suffered a brain bleed
OL,16,Fwhile on a call to occupational health
OL,17,Fto discuss his return to work.
