OL,3,CColleagues 'let down' hospital
OL,4,Cemployee who died after collapsing on
OL,5,Cwork call
OL,7,FThe 65-year-old father of three was a
OL,8,Fmanager at University Hospital
OL,9,FSouthampton, responsible for planning
OL,10,Fand modernisation.
OL,12,FMr Ginger had been off work for a
OL,13,Fwhile and had some serious health
OL,14,Fissues, including heart attacks.
OL,16,FOccupational nurse Jackie Chatteron,
OL,17,Fwho had been speaking to Mr Ginger
OL,18,Fwhen he collapsed, sent a Teams
OL,19,Fmessage about the incident to another
OL,20,Fcolleague before calling 999.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
