OL,7,FIt was 6 hours before his family found
OL,8,Fhim and called an ambulance. The
OL,9,Fcoroner recorded a verdict of natural
OL,10,Fcauses but said that she had never
OL,11,Fcome across anything like this in over
OL,12,F30 years as a coroner.
OL,14,FThe family of Nicholas Ginger listened
OL,15,Fto three days of evidence about their
OL,16,F65-year-old father.
OL,18,FHis daughter Maria Burgess said: "It's
OL,19,Fbeen quite an ordeal but (the coroner)
OL,20,Fwas exceptional. She was fair and very
OL,21,Fempathetic.
