OL,7,F"I felt she did an incredible job in
OL,8,Fan extremely difficult situation she
OL,9,Fsaid she'd never come across anything
OL,10,Fquite like it in more than 30 years of
OL,11,Fdoing her job which speaks volumes for
OL,12,Fthe shocking nature of what's
OL,13,Foccurred."
OL,15,FThis afternoon, the coroner said she
OL,16,Ffound it "impossible to reconcile the
OL,17,Fvarious strands of evidence."
OL,19,FThe court heard that two conflicting
OL,20,Freports of Mr Ginger final hours were
OL,21,Fgiven by Southampton hospital.
