OL,7,FOccupational health confirmed that he
OL,8,Fhad suffered an acute medical episode,
OL,9,Fbut a patient safety report said he
OL,10,Fhad not.
OL,12,FThe family heard Mr Ginger was talking
OL,13,Fto nurse Jackie Chatterton from
OL,14,Foccupational health in November 2022
OL,15,Fwhen he disappeared from the screen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
