OL,7,FMs Chatterton also previously told the
OL,8,Fhearing she thought it would be
OL,9,Fconfusing to call an ambulance from
OL,10,Fher location in Southport and realised
OL,11,Fin hindsight she should have called an
OL,12,Fambulance.
OL,14,FThe coroner has told Southampton
OL,15,Fhospital to re-visit their
OL,16,Finvestigation, taking into account the
OL,17,Foccupational health report.
