OL,7,FA spokesperson for University Hospital
OL,8,FSouthampton said: "We are deeply
OL,9,Fsaddened by the death of our valued
OL,10,Fcolleague and our thoughts and
OL,11,Fsympathies remain with Mr Ginger's
OL,12,Ffamily.
OL,14,F"The circumstances surrounding Mr
OL,15,FGinger's death were investigated and
OL,16,Freviewed, and as a result we have
OL,17,Fintroduced a series of improvements to
OL,18,Four Occupational Health processes and
OL,19,Fguidance, which have also been shared
OL,20,Fwith our healthcare partners across
OL,21,Four system.
